Contains all files related to our second programming assignment.

Description of assignment:
finish implementing fig.06.15.c to make it work as intended (based on the comments and behavior described in the book).
This will require you to find and complete the incomplete scan_fraction() code from fig.06.10.c.
It will require you to complete the stubbed functions so that their functionality is completed. 
Note what the book says about unit testing and integration testing. Tackle one part at a time.

Complete the code and integrate into code base for project.

Demonstrate the code working from command line and document in report.
